front.title: •Daultay Dofine
front.gametext: At start of your draw phase, if you have no cards in your Force Pile may activate up to two Force. If your just drawn destiny was a destroyer droid or battle droid, once per turn you may take that card into hand to cancel that destiny and re-draw.
front.lore: Neimoidian Trade Federation captain who gained his current position through political backstabbing and family connections. Not favored by Darth Sidious.

combo: Daultay Dofine + Nute Gunray + Blockade Flagship: Bridge + destroyer droids/battle droids
